<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
  </head>

  <body>
    <p>Dear Customer,</p>

    <p>
      We regret to inform you that your account statement could not be generated at this time.
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>Statement Details:</strong><br>
      Account Number: <%= @statement.account_number %><br>
      Period: <%= @statement.from_date %> to <%= @statement.to_date %>
    </p>

    <% if @error.present? %>
      <p>
        <strong>Reason:</strong><br>
        <%= @error %>
      </p>
    <% end %>

    <p>
      This may be due to a temporary system issue or incomplete information.
      Please try again later.
    </p>

    <p>
      If the problem persists, kindly contact our support team and quote your
      <strong>Statement Reference ID:</strong> <%= @statement.id %>.
    </p>

    <p>
      We apologize for the inconvenience caused.
    </p>

    <p>
      Regards,<br>
      <strong>BNB Support Team</strong>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
